A blog site which started out as a simple app to learn Flask, now evolved into my pet project. I write articles and some programming stuff for this. Nearly a full-fledged indie blog site with subscriptions (free, for notifying), well-designed UI, comments and ratings on posts, audio versions and more. Please check out and recommend to whoever you think might be interested.

Hosted on Koyeb: https://shetty777.koyeb.app/
